  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section class="py-12 sm:py-16 bg-base-200">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-8 sm:mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-base-content mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-base-content/70 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Everything you need to know about Find a Coach</p>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <!-- FAQ Items -->
          <div class="collapse collapse-arrow bg-base-100">
            <input type="radio" name="faq-accordion" checked="checked" />
            <div class="collapse-title text-lg font-medium">
              Why did you create Find a Coach, and why do you maintain it?
            </div>
            <div class="collapse-content">
              <p class="text-base-content/80">
                I ❤️ coaching. There's nothing like seeing that spark in someone's eyes when they realize they have the power to change their life. Suddenly, things that felt impossible become possible.<br/>
                <br/>
                I ❤️ <a href="https://rubyonrails.org/" class="link">Ruby on Rails</a> and how its changing SW developement for over 20+ years.
                I wanted to have a real hands on experience with this framework.<br/>
                <br/>
                It started during my ACC certification as I wanted to know how many pro bono and how many paid hours of coaching I have provided.
                So I decided to join my two passions and create Find a Coach.<br/>
                <br/>
                I maintain it because I want to have a tool that I would like to use myself and I want to share it with other coaches.<br/>
                <br/>
                Simple, barebone but effective.
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="collapse collapse-arrow bg-base-100">
            <input type="radio" name="faq-accordion" />
            <div class="collapse-title text-lg font-medium">
              How secure is my client data?
            </div>
            <div class="collapse-content">
              <p class="text-base-content/80">
                Your personal data is encrypted in our database using the same methods banks rely on.<br/>
                <br/>
                All passwords are safely hashed with bcrypt, so they can never be read or stolen in plain text.<br/>
                <br/>
                Every connection runs over HTTPS, keeping your information safe while it travels online.<br/>
                <br/>
                Rails automatically protects you from common attacks such as fake form submissions (CSRF) and malicious scripts (XSS).<br/>
                <br/>
                These protections work silently in the background, so you can use our service with confidence.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="collapse collapse-arrow bg-base-100">
            <input type="radio" name="faq-accordion" />
            <div class="collapse-title text-lg font-medium">
              Can I customize my coach profile page?
            </div>
            <div class="collapse-content">
              <p class="text-base-content/80">
                No, not at the moment.<br/>
                <br/>
                If you have a particular idea that would help you, please <%= link_to "contact me", findacoach_contact_path, class:"link" %>.<br/>
                <br/>
                I promise I will consider your proposal.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="collapse collapse-arrow bg-base-100">
            <input type="radio" name="faq-accordion" />
            <div class="collapse-title text-lg font-medium">
              When will the paid plan be available, and how will it affect the free plan?
            </div>
            <div class="collapse-content">
              <p class="text-base-content/80">
                Not decided yet when the paid plan will be launched.
                Find a Coach needs to have enough users before I can start considering a paid version.<br/>
                <br/>
                When paid version will be available, free version will stay.
                Users will not lose access to any free plan features <br/>
                <br/>
                All new features (unless too costly) will be available in a free plan so everybody can benefit from those.<br/>
                <br/>
                The paid plan will be for coaches who already have an established practice and can afford to pay.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="collapse collapse-arrow bg-base-100">
            <input type="radio" name="faq-accordion" />
            <div class="collapse-title text-lg font-medium">
              What types of coaching does it support?
            </div>
            <div class="collapse-content">
              <p class="text-base-content/80">
                Find a Coach is designed with pure <a href="https://coachingfederation.org" class="link">ICF</a> based coaching in mind.<br/>
                <br/>
                 In spirit, this means no prepaid programs — just pure coaching, guiding clients, and helping them achieve the goals they define.<br/>
                <br/>
                But it can be used for all types of professional coaching including life coaching, business coaching, 
                executive coaching, career coaching, wellness coaching, and more.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
